HEADWORD: Derringer
<hw>Der"rin*ger</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From the American
inventor.]</ety> <def>A kind of short-barreled pocket pistol, of very
large caliber, often carrying a half-ounce ball.</def>⟦br⟧
